@macro
$# Macro Functions

  NetBox can be controlled from FAR macros using Plugin.Call.

  General format:
    Plugin.Call("{GUID}", <Function>, <Parameters>...)

  #Main plugin GUID:#
    {42E4AEB1-A230-44F4-B33C-F195BB654931}

  #Available functions:#

    "Menu" - Open configuration menu.
    "Main" - Open main configuration dialog.
    "Log" - Open logging configuration.
    "Hrc" - Open session/protocol configuration.
    "Reload" - Reload plugin configuration and sessions.
    "Status", [0|1] - Get or set plugin status (disable/enable).
    "SaveSettings" - Save current settings.

    "Types", "Menu" - Show file type selection menu.
    "Types", "List" - Get list of available types.
    "Types", "Get" - Get current file type and group.
    "Types", "Set", <Type> - Set file type for current file.

    "Brackets", "Match" - Find matching bracket.
    "Brackets", "SelectAll" - Select block including brackets.
    "Brackets", "SelectIn" - Select content between brackets.

    "Region", "Select" - Select current region.
    "Region", "Show" - Show region information.
    "Region", "List" - Get region description.

    "Functions", "Show" - Show function list.
    "Functions", "Find" - Find function under cursor.
    "Functions", "List" - Get all functions array.

    "Errors", "Show" - Show error list.
    "Errors", "List" - Get all errors array.

    "Editor", "Refresh" - Refresh syntax highlighting.
    "Editor", "Status", [0|1] - Get/set editor-specific status.
    "Editor", "CrossVisible", [style] - Control crosshair display.
    "Editor", "Pair", [0|1] - Show/hide paired elements.
    "Editor", "Syntax", [0|1] - Show/hide syntax coloring.
    "Editor", "Progress" - Get current parsing progress.

@author
$# About NetBox

  NetBox is a plugin for FAR Manager providing access to remote
  file systems via various protocols.

  #Home page:#
     https://github.com/NetBox-WinSCP/NetBox

  #Based on:#
     WinSCP (https://winscp.net/)
     FileZilla (https://filezilla-project.org/)
     PuTTY (https://www.putty.org/)
     OpenSSL (https://openssl.org/)
     neon (https://notroj.github.io/neon/)
     libs3 (https://github.com/bji/libs3)

  #License:#
     GPL v3 or later (NetBox, WinSCP)
     LGPL v2.1+ (FileZilla)
     MIT (some components)

  #Contributors:#
     See project repository for full list of authors and contributors.

@end
